## Routing & Payment Methods

### Available Routes
- `/vabank/[idagen]` - Virtual Account payment method
- `/ewallet/[idagen]` - E-Wallet payment method
- `/qris/[idagen]` - QRIS payment method
- `/retail/[idagen]` - Retail Outlet payment method

### Flow
1. Android WebView mengakses base route (e.g., `/vabank`) dengan `Authorization` header
2. Middleware decode header dan extract `idagen`
3. Redirect ke `/[paymentMethod]/[idagen]`
4. Page menampilkan `DepositForm` dengan:
   - `defaultPaymentMethod` sesuai route
   - `hidePaymentMethodSelect={true}` (tidak bisa ganti metode)
   - `idagen` dari URL params (dikirim ke backend)

